Package com.jimmyselectronics.necchi

Class SampleBarcodeScannerListener

java.lang.Object
com.jimmyselectronics.necchi.SampleBarcodeScannerListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
AbstractDeviceListener, BarcodeScannerListener
public class SampleBarcodeScannerListener extends Object implements BarcodeScannerListener
This is a sample of how one could create a class to listen for events emanating from a barcode scanner. This sample only reacts to "turnedOn", "turnedOff", and "barcodeScanned" events. You can see this class in action by running the test suite in SampleBarcodeScannerDemo.
